reviewText: The son character gets into situations that are funny yet a learning situation.  She's spunky but lovable.  The artists in these cartoons have drawn them so beautifully.  The scenes and backgrounds are heavenly.  I wish I could visit this little area in this cartoon!
i enjoyed watching all of the series. wish they'd bring the show back :( its a shame that its not aired
I can't wait for my daughter to be able to watch the series...I will always be a fan and hopefully someday I can go see where the orin/ films were made in Edward Island....
